Aug 23, 2010

#1

Locked the handle bars when I parked it last night and now I cannot get the key to turn from the locked position. I am pushing the key straight down as always before turning it but still no luck. I have a 05 Busa. Anyone ever experienced this before?? Thanks for your support.

Steve
